{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbccce9f3-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s4370f"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4370f"},"text":"§ 4370f.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Availability of funds after expiration of period for liquidating obligations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For fiscal year 2001 and thereafter, the obligated balances of sums available in multiple-year appropriations accounts shall remain available through the seventh fiscal year after their period of availability has expired for liquidating obligations made during the period of availability.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbccce9f4-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/377/s1/a/1/tIII"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–377, § 1(a)(1) [title III]","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2000-10-27"},"text":"Oct. 27, 2000","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/114/1441"},"text":"114 Stat. 1441","children":[],"tail":", 1441A–44.)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbccce9f5-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbccce9f6-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idbccce9f7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was enacted as part of the Departments of Veterans Affairs and Housing and Urban Development, and Independent Agencies Appropriations Act, 2001, and not as part of the National Environmental Policy Act of 1969 which comprises this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
